<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM7.6">
<l>pōyttīrtta māṭātē niṉṟa puṇarmarutañ</l>
<l>cāyttīrttāṉ kaittalattē yēṟik kuṭikoṇṭu</l>
<l>cēyttīrtta māyniṉṟa ceṅkaṇmāl taṉṉuṭaiya</l>
<l>vāyttīrttam pāyntāṭa vallāy valampuriyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O right-spiralled [conch]! You are capable of diving and bathing</l>
<l>in the distant water that is the saliva of the red-eyed Māl</l>
<l>having climbed and settled in the palm of [the Lord] who broke and</l>
<l>pulled down the entwined Arjun trees,</l>
<l rend="indent">instead of going [far] to bathe in holy water!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
